      <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z166"/>
      <p>Zombies are corpses reanimated through dark and sinister magic.<a href="img/MonstersT-Z.Zombie.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersT-Z.Zombie.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p>Because of their utter lack of intelligence, the instructions given to a newly created zombie must be very simple.</p>
      <div class="sect2" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="title"><a name="id2249675"/>Creating A Zombie</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
          <div class="keyword">monsterinfo</div>
        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z167"/>
        <p>'Zombie' is an acquired template that can be added to any corporeal creature (other than an undead) that has a skeletal system (referred to hereafter as the base creature).</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2249699"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z168"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Size and Type:</strong></span> The creature's type changes to undead. It retains any subtypes except alignment subtypes and subtypes that indicate kind. It does not gain the augmented subtype. It uses all the base creature's statistics and special abilities except as noted here.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2249731"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z169"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Hit Dice:</strong></span> Drop any Hit Dice from class levels (to a minimum of 1), double the number of Hit Dice left, and raise them to d12s. If the base creature has more than 10 Hit Dice (not counting those gained with experience), it can't be made into a zombie with the <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch43.html#SpellsA-B15">animate dead</a></em></span> spell.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2249774"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z170"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Speed:</strong></span> If the base creature can fly, its maneuverability rating drops to clumsy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2249803"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z171"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Armor Class:</strong></span> Natural armor bonus increases by a number based on the zombie's size:</p>
          <table width="100%" border="1" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="2" frame="void" rules="rows" id="id2249830">
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><p>Tiny or smaller</p></td> <td><p>+0</p></td>

</tr>
              <tr><td><p>Small</p></td>
<td><p>+1</p></td>

</tr>
              <tr><td><p>Medium</p></td>
<td><p>+2</p></td>

</tr>
              <tr><td><p>Large</p></td>
<td><p>+3</p></td>

</tr>
              <tr><td><p>Huge</p></td>
<td><p>+4</p></td>

</tr>
              <tr><td><p>Gargantuan</p></td>
<td><p>+7</p></td>

</tr>
              <tr><td><p>Colossal</p></td>
<td><p>+11</p></td>

</tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2250028"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z172"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Base Attack:</strong></span> A zombie has a base attack bonus equal to 1/2 its Hit Dice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2250057"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z173"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Attacks:</strong></span> A zombie retains all the natural weapons, manufactured weapon attacks, and weapon proficiencies of the base creature. A zombie also gains a slam attack.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2250156"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z174"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Damage:</strong></span> Natural and manufactured weapons deal damage normally. A slam attack deals damage depending on the zombie's size. (Use the base creature's slam damage if it's better.)</p>
