          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersT-Z180"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Feats:</strong></span> A zombie loses all feats of the base creature and gains <a href="ch17s03.html#Feats361">Toughness</a>.</p>
